### Stream Messages with Anthropic SDK (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-typescript/blob/main/helpers.md

Initiates a streaming message request using the Anthropic SDK. It returns a MessageStream object that can be iterated over or used with event listeners to process messages as they arrive. Alternatively, stream: true can be used with create for direct async iteration over chunks.

```typescript
anthropic.messages.stream({ … }, options?): MessageStream
```

