### Stream Anthropic Messages

Source: https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-typescript/blob/main/README.md

Shows how to receive streaming responses from the Anthropic API using TypeScript. This approach is useful for real-time interactions.

```ts
import Anthropic from '@anthropic-ai/sdk';

const client = new Anthropic();

const stream = await client.messages.create({
  max_tokens: 1024,
  messages: [{ role: 'user', content: 'Hello, Claude' }],
  model: 'claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929',
  stream: true,
});
for await (const messageStreamEvent of stream) {
  console.log(messageStreamEvent.type);
}
```

