### Handle Anthropic Streaming Responses with Helpers

Source: https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-typescript/blob/main/README.md

Demonstrates using convenience helpers for streaming messages with the Anthropic SDK. This includes event handlers for different message parts.

```ts
import Anthropic from '@anthropic-ai/sdk';

const anthropic = new Anthropic();

async function main() {
  const stream = anthropic.messages
    .stream({
      model: 'claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929',
      max_tokens: 1024,
      messages: [
        {
          role: 'user',
          content: 'Say hello there!',
        },
      ],
    })
    .on('text', (text) => {
      console.log(text);
    });

  const message = await stream.finalMessage();
  console.log(message);
}

main();
```

