### Handle Files using Node.js Streams

Source: https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-typescript/blob/main/MIGRATION.md

Illustrates the removal of the deprecated `fileFromPath` helper and the recommendation to use native Node.js streams for file handling. For Bun environments, `Bun.file` is suggested as an alternative.

```typescript
// Before
Anthropic.fileFromPath('path/to/file');

// After
import fs from 'fs';
fs.createReadStream('path/to/file');
```

